  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And soon we realized that we are left to our own devices.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I was able to go on a work detail, and they took me on a work detail one night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was early January.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, they brought us back in the middle of the night, not allowing us to finish the shift.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Oh, I have to backtrack because we realized that they were going to liquidate the ghetto because there were-- there were some comings and goings in the ghetto, and there was a lot of activity.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So I decided that I am not going to let my younger sister stick around and, and, and be subjected to this liquidation of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told her that I'm going to send her to these friends of ours.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Their name was Loszek, L-O-S-Z-E-K.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, you will go to the Loszeks, and you will tell them to keep you until Henryk can come for you, for them to get in touch with Henryk.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember she had a blue coat, and she had a muff.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember when we left very early on, when we went to Konskie, my mother sewed into that muff, of all the ludicrous things, optimistically, her Prudential life insurance-- it was Prudential, the same name as we have here-- my mother's and my father's life insurance, a deed to the property my father had bought in Israel, and a string of real seeded pearls.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I gave my sister the muff, and I told her how important that muff was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was dusk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I took her to a, not a gate, but a, a-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I can't think of the word.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
